{"tid":1015481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友話之後每次扑完野要收番我錢","createTime":"2019-02-10T04:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T05:25:22.000Z","uid":213537,"like":50,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e26abb9a86710459adb68fd9f56587192c0a6757","tid":1015481,"uid":213537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"事源我老豆老母因為三十結婚週年紀念所以去左個長trip所以屋企長期冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住呢排成日帶條女上我度啪啪啪了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢尋日無差差同我講話突然覺得自己好cheap 話自己好似仲cheap 過隻雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我就安撫佢話無啲咁嘅事<br />\n叫佢唔好亂諗野 再同佢講只要唔好當自己係雞你就只係會同男朋友扑野嘅女朋友<br />\n<br />\n然之後佢就開始發曬顛話自己根本就係隻免費雞 話每次搞完都要收番我五舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n我好理性咁同佢講由你收我錢果刻開始 <br />\n你就真係會由我女朋友昇華成為一隻雞<br />\n而且只值五舊水嘅雞🐔<br />\n<br />\n佢同我講因為我係佢男朋友所以先有discount<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話唔想再縱我攪到我認為世上係有免費午餐免費雞。。。<br />\n我真係一頭冒水 再同佢理論話扑野係情侶間係好平常嘅事 而且你都成日有得高潮 你每次都搞得咁爽 我咁好服務你仲要收返我錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但最後佢都格硬係我銀包拎走左五百蚊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係咁佢變左做隻雞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁不過我又真係一直當佢係雞嘅<br />\n所以都唔怪得佢會咁諗嘅<br />\n屌你老母死臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b357e2b0447235a685e057b827b7a55